data.meta_description: Books - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. This document appears to be a list of book titles and their authors. It includes over 200 entries with the format of "Books, Author, Title". The list includes books from a wide range of genres including fiction, non-fiction, children's books, and more. The authors listed range from well-known authors like Mitch Albom, Isabel Allende, and Chris Van Allsburg to lesser known authors.
